  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>rats...piles</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>The piles of Venice are the heavy beams\n        which support the buildings from sinking into the soft\n        sea-bed of the Adriatic sea. Rats gnawed at these wooden\n        piles, sometimes causing a building to collapse.</font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "rats...piles The piles of Venice are the heavy beams which support the buildings from sinking into the soft sea-bed of the Adriatic sea. Rats gnawed at these wooden piles, sometimes causing a building to collapse. reference topics back to \"Burbank\"",
